rComments: Nicole is so funny and interesting. She is a very approachable lecturer and clearly makes an effort to cover many different perspectives and mediums. Highly recommended

I had her for Intro to the Nude and Style Wars. She hands you an A+ while keeping the class at a demanding level. She basically confers critical thinking upon those who are willing to get past their own biases and recognize issues/critiques within the institution of art. Highly Recommended!!!

This class is great! Interesting way to learn history if you are visually/art oriented. Nicole lets you have a full sheet of notes for the midterm and final, so its easy to ace (you can even write out your whole essay on one side). Nicole is also humorous and hip, you are not being taught by a droning, ancient professor!

this class was so hard. it would seem easy since it was an intro class, but there was so much useless work involved and exams that you could not study for. i failed miserably while putting in a considerable amount of effort =[
